      "content": "i know it's grief. i feel it every single second. it just feels like there is no version of the future where i am okay. it's like the world is just moving on without me and i'm just stuck in this dark hole. it would be so much easier if i just didn't have to feel this anymore. do you think it ever actually stops? or is this just what life is now?",
